### Subir PDF (multipart: chat_id + file)
POST {{dpsBase}}/create-document
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="chat_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="A_Avión_de_Caza_Multirrol_F-X_Halcón_Boreal_digital.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../../test_documents/general/A_Arte_y_Cultura_digital.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--


### Subir DOCX
POST {{dpsBase}}/create-document
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="chat_id"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="B_El_niño_que_no_sabía_envejecer_digital.docx"
